summary: Small SM theme package, featuring torture room and pillar of restrain at Solitude Proudspire Manor.
descriptionHtml:
This mod is just a practice work for the quest system and scene control stuffs. As usual, a small (very small) quest will lead you to the functions of the mod. For start, go in game and wait for 10 seconds, you should hear a voice and see the screen shacking.

If you cannot run this mod....forget it.^_^.
or check out my other mods:

Multiple Marriages and Changing Spouse Outfits - WIP
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=9378

NPC Clothes Changer and Maintainer
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=11662

the quest scene could be halted sometime, if has problem, just use console command to jump over the quest.

setstage dudestiasmintroq 45
author: Dudestia_wchen
